"ROCKET 5T" and "UBIQUITI NETWORKS Â© 2012" is silkscreened on the board. :Appears to be [[Atheros]] AR7370 (AR9344 rev2) + AR9280 based..
This device has two Ethernet ports. The main port (also the PoE input) :is 1GbE (10/100/1000), the secondary port is FE (10/100) only.
Presumed 00:27:22 (''[[Ubiquiti Networks]]'') OUI (on MAC label affixed :to the FCC EUT and in the FCC QSG) May also use a DC:9F:DB OUI (in original filing [FCC ID: SWX-RM5T])
